      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example boasts impeccable mechanical provenance, with rod bearings and throttle actuators preemptively serviced to ensure long-term kinetic integrity. The 6-speed manual transmission offers tactile, short-throw engagement, paired with a factory-spec carbon fiber roof for a significantly lowered center of gravity. The chassis remains exceptionally taut, showing zero bushing deflection or subframe fatigue, while the paint retains its original depth and luster. Equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and a functional M-variable differential lock, this unit delivers surgical turn-in and perfectly linear power delivery. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
