      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning enthusiast. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-original luster, enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; you will find zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks across the entire body. The wheels are flawless, with no curb rash, wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The high-grade leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear, creasing, or sun fading. It has never been smoked in and remains pet-free, retaining that fresh, new-car scent. Every technological feature\u2014from the high-fidelity surround sound system to the advanced navigation and heated seating\u2014operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive, folder-bound service history documenting every oil change and inspection performed exclusively by certified technicians. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of corrosion or road wear. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously curated piece of machinery that drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
